  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※The game allows for custom buttons, including the controller and keyboard and mouse, and the controller has vibration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※If the controller does not respond, please follow the following settings: right-click the game name → Properties → Controller → Use default settings or Disable Steam Input.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【The game currently has two stages, and Stage 3 will be updated in early 2026. The original price will increase as more content is added.】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SLASHING NIGHT</strong> is a fast-paced pure action Devil May Cry-like game, fully developed and self-published by me using Unity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can enjoy exhilarating combat with seamless real-time weapon switching to perform free aerial and ground combos. The game offers three difficulty levels. Since the goal is to deliver a stylish and free combat experience, high difficulty is not the core focus. This game is perfect for players who love nonstop, satisfying battles. Key binding customization is supported.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Current Weapons]</strong><br>Melee: Katana, Martial Arts, Scythe<br>Ranged: Revolver</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Current Total Skill Count]</strong><br>Around 33, including JC (Jump Cancel / Step on enemy midair), double jump, teleport, and aerial dodge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Featured Systems]</strong><br>• <strong>Damage Rate Evaluation System:</strong> Performing combos with different weapons and skills increases your rating and damage, up to x1.5.<br>• <strong>Magic Shield:</strong> Works like instant parry but cannot be used preemptively. When activated right before taking a hit, nearby enemies are slowed.<br>• <strong>Perfect Dodge:</strong> Regular dodge won’t trigger it. Only dodging right before being hit activates it, slowing down surrounding enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Current Game Progress]</strong><br>Stages: 2 (final version will have 5)<br>Playtime: About 45 minutes or more<br>Enemy Types: 5</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is still being updated.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Magic shield and perfect dodge can slow down the enemy's movements. Take this opportunity to counterattack the enemy!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/cf7da4c4118abef00c3c7f39c2dd7d16.poster.avif?t=1765108231\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/cf7da4c4118abef00c3c7f39c2dd7d16.webm?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/cf7da4c4118abef00c3c7f39c2dd7d16.mp4?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/afd79619de6c0d3ed93763f0c3fb4fe0.poster.avif?t=1765108231\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/afd79619de6c0d3ed93763f0c3fb4fe0.webm?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/afd79619de6c0d3ed93763f0c3fb4fe0.mp4?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/e57aeb9566052e20b1af437df113cdcf.poster.avif?t=1765108231\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/e57aeb9566052e20b1af437df113cdcf.webm?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/e57aeb9566052e20b1af437df113cdcf.mp4?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use stepping on enemies, double jump, teleport, and air dodge to perform gorgeous aerial combos. Aerial attacks can increase the damage rate more easily.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/842ff2567e03a5276fc3305462f8a561.poster.avif?t=1765108231\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/842ff2567e03a5276fc3305462f8a561.webm?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/842ff2567e03a5276fc3305462f8a561.mp4?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Consume energy to release high-damage skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/089dd554874fef05448822f4dd68d8fc.poster.avif?t=1765108231\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/089dd554874fef05448822f4dd68d8fc.webm?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/089dd554874fef05448822f4dd68d8fc.mp4?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Switch between different weapons and perform gorgeous combos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/5846805fb69ad329b4a06f4ff0aecf8b.poster.avif?t=1765108231\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/5846805fb69ad329b4a06f4ff0aecf8b.webm?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/5846805fb69ad329b4a06f4ff0aecf8b.mp4?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/2fa4d0eb8a7d35c091b3723397789aa4.poster.avif?t=1765108231\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/2fa4d0eb8a7d35c091b3723397789aa4.webm?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/2fa4d0eb8a7d35c091b3723397789aa4.mp4?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
